text:
A report by @NDTV claiming the shortage of the #COVID19 #vaccine in #Rajasthan went viral on social media. It was later found that there is no shortage of vaccine in the state & according to the @MoHFW_INDIA, the state was supplied with 37.61 lakh doses. 
#CallingItOut #FakeNews https://t.co/VLLOtHCqhv
